      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776192402171,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🔄 Fluxo Principal: Consulta de Score",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.4666666666666666
    },
    {
      "id": "flow-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 283.3240884211855,
      "y": 964.6653095470188,
      "width": 1070,
      "height": 154,
      "text": "1.  Client → web-app: submit {chain, address}\n2.  web-app → api-gateway: POST /analysis  (JWT auth)\n3.  api-gateway: cria AnalysisRequest (PENDING), valida usage limit via users service (HTTP)\n4.  api-gateway → RabbitMQ: publica wallet.data.requested\n5.  data-search: consome evento, checa Redis cache → miss: busca Etherscan → normaliza → armazena Redis (20min TTL)\n6.  data-search → RabbitMQ: publica wallet.data.cached\n7.  process-data-ia: consome evento, verifica score salvo (24h TTL) → válido: reutiliza | expirado: chama AI model\n8.  process-data-ia → RabbitMQ: publica wallet.score.calculated (score + factors + metadata)\n9.  api-gateway: consome resultado → atualiza AnalysisRequest (COMPLETED) → publica user.analysis.consumed\n10. users: consome user.analysis.consumed → incrementa contador mensal\n11. data-indexing: consome wallet.data.cached + wallet.score.calculated → indexa no Meilisearch\n12. Client: poll GET /analysis/{id} → recebe score (0-100), reasoning, fatores positivos e de risco",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 10003,
      "version": 22,
      "versionNonce": 1814003452,
      "index": "b0J",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "groupIds": [
        "U4voyHzDQojXH075Z76Mx"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776192402171,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.  Client → web-app: submit {chain, address}\n2.  web-app → api-gateway: POST /analysis  (JWT auth)\n3.  api-gateway: cria AnalysisRequest (PENDING), valida usage limit via users service (HTTP)\n4.  api-gateway → RabbitMQ: publica wallet.data.requested\n5.  data-search: consome evento, checa Redis cache → miss: busca Etherscan → normaliza → armazena Redis (20min TTL)\n6.  data-search → RabbitMQ: publica wallet.data.cached\n7.  process-data-ia: consome evento, verifica score salvo (24h TTL) → válido: reutiliza | expirado: chama AI model\n8.  process-data-ia → RabbitMQ: publica wallet.score.calculated (score + factors + metadata)\n9.  api-gateway: consome resultado → atualiza AnalysisRequest (COMPLETED) → publica user.analysis.consumed\n10. users: consome user.analysis.consumed → incrementa contador mensal\n11. data-indexing: consome wallet.data.cached + wallet.score.calculated → indexa no Meilisearch\n12. Client: poll GET /analysis/{id} → recebe score (0-100), reasoning, fatores positivos e de risco",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.0694444444444444
    },
